you to R, RStudio, and the <em><a href=\"https://www.tidyverse.org/\">tidyverse</a></em>, a collection of R packages designed to work together to make data science fast, fluent, and fun. Suitable for readers with no previous programming experience, R for Data Science is designed to get you doing data science as quickly as possible.</p>","updatedAt":"2017-10-11T18:44:36.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"tleb/awesome-mastodon","categoryHTML":"<h2>Tools</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://framagit.org/luc/last\">Last</a> - Aggregate toots on a web page providing Atom feed and an epub (Perl).</li>","updatedAt":"2017-10-11T18:31:51.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"daviddias/awesome-hacking-locations","categoryHTML":"<h2>Massachusetts </h2><h4>Diesel Cafe</h4>","itemHTML":"<li>Contact <a href=\"https://twitter.com/richlitt\">@richlitt</a> for wifi password if needed.</li>","updatedAt":"2017-10-11T17:22:50.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"daviddias/awesome-hacking-locations","categoryHTML":"<h2>Massachusetts </h2><h4>Diesel Cafe</h4>","itemHTML":"<li>You get 45m of free wifi per day. More if you know what you're doing ;) (but $14/mo for wifi is worth it if you hack there often)</li>","updatedAt":"2017-10-11T17:22:50.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"daviddias/awesome-hacking-locations","categoryHTML":"<h2>Massachusetts </h2><h4>Diesel Cafe</h4>","itemHTML":"<li>Using IPFS will get you kicked off their network in ~2hr (FYI).</li>","updatedAt":"2017-10-11T17:22:50.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"matteofigus/awesome-speaking","categoryHTML":"<h2>Blog Posts</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.samjarman.co.nz/blog/speaking-gigs\">How To Get Speaking Engagements</a> - by <strong>Sam Jarman</strong></li>","updatedAt":"2017-10-11T17:13:49.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"mojoaxel/awesome-regression-testing","categoryHTML":"<h2>Slideshows, talks and videos</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://youtu.be/CBBiJ6YlXLc\">Visual Regression Testing with Shoov</a> - How to setup shoov and get your first test wri